Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.items.Item
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bacon, CactusSeed, Carrot, CarrotSeed, ChickenFeed, CowFeed, Cucumber, CucumberSeed, Egg, Fertilizer, Milk, PigFeed, Potatoe, PotatoeSeed, PricklyPear, Watermelon, WatermelonSeed, Wheat, WheatSeed

    public abstract class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    Items are used to plant crops, feed animals, and can be harvested from crops and animals and sold at the store.
